- 2.0.5 | Apr 05 2026:

  -- Security --

  [Fix] Add symlink guards on cursor read in _tlog_parse_cursor() and
      tlog_journal_read() — prevents symlink-following on cursor files,
      journal cursor files, and journal timestamp files (3 read sites)
  [Fix] Add symlink guards on stale-protection touch in tlog_read() and
      tlog_journal_read() — prevents mtime modification of symlink targets
      (3 touch sites)
  [New] 6 BATS tests for symlink detection, cursor rebuild, target
      protection, stale-protection skip, and false-positive verification
  [Change] CI: batsman 1.4.0 → 1.4.1; CI workflow pin v1.0.3 → v1.4.1

  -- Changes --

  [Change] Version bump 2.0.4 → 2.0.5
  [Change] README: update threat model (symlink attack now mitigated),
      test count 196 → 206
